    "authors": ["Manual Tester"],
    "description": "The type is `tutorial`, so the `tutorial` block below is the one active block. The `reference_images` and `daz3d` blocks are **foreign payload** this file is merely custodian of ([[plugins#plugin-blocks]], A4.2/#82): inactive, and -- crucially -- **never made active this session**, so the block persistence invariant **carries them verbatim** on save, byte-for-byte. Contrast a block that was switched *to* and then *away* from (claimed-then-abandoned), which would instead be dropped on save. Open, save untouched, and both foreign blocks must survive; switch the type to `reference_images` and back to `tutorial`, and only *then* does `reference_images` become claimed and drop on the next save."
  },
